<title>USA: Technology Modeling sets share buyback.</title>
<headline>Technology Modeling sets share buyback.</headline>
<dateline>SUNNYVALE, Calif. 1997-04-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>Technology Modeling Associates Inc said on Thursday its board authorised the repurchase of up to one million shares of its common stock for cash from time to time at market prices.</p>
<p>Purchases would be made in the open market depending upon both market and business conditions, the company said.</p>
<p>Technology Modeling said it was able to repurchase shares because of its strong cash position and there was no time limit to the buyback program.</p>
<p>The company develops and licenses physical simulation software for integrated circuit design and manufacturing.</p>
<p>((New York newsdesk 212-859-1610))</p>
